Package org.opensocial.data

Class Summary
OpenSocialActivity Class representing the OpenSocialActivity object which is used in the REST calls for fetching and creating activities
OpenSocialAppData An object representing OpenSocial App Data; extends OpenSocialObject class by adding a convenience method for getting the data value associated with a particular key for a particular user.
OpenSocialField An object representing a single property of an OpenSocial entity.
OpenSocialObject An object representing a generic, extensible OpenSocial entity.
OpenSocialPerson An object representing a person in an OpenSocial environment; extends OpenSocialObject class by adding convenience methods for easily accessing special fields unique to instances of this class.
 

Exception Summary
OpenSocialException A generic exception to be thrown when an unexpected or otherwise erroneous event or condition forces an operation or method to terminate during execution.
